s create a misty veil that rises high into the air. And if you\'re lucky, you might even spot a rainbow or two!\\n\\nBut don\'t just take our word for it! Our recent tour group, consisting of a couple and their two kids (aged 3 and 5), had an absolute blast on their 3-hour boat ride under the falls. The kids were mesmerized by the sights and sounds of the wild, and the adults were thrilled by the sheer beauty of it all.\\n\\nSo why wait? Come and experience the magic of Murchison Falls National Park for yourself. With its incredible wildlife, stunning natural beauty, and unforgettable experiences, this park is a must-visit destination for any nature lover or adventure seeker.\\n\\nBook your tour today and get ready for the ultimate African adventure!\", \"version\": 1, \"category\": \"news\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1742929569/murchison-falls_kos0uo.webp\", \"videoUrl\": \"https://youtu.be/MvwcnVbhymY\", \"createdAt\": \"2025-03-25T19:09:03.134Z\", \"createdBy\": null, \"deletedAt\": null, \"deletedBy\": null, \"isDeleted\": false, \"updatedAt\": \"2025-03-25T19:09:03.134Z\", \"updatedBy\": null}',NULL,'::ffff:127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/134.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/134.0.0.0',5),(58,'2025-03-25 19:38:03.436723','2025-03-25 19:38:03.436723',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,'create','Created new admin','admin',NULL,NULL,'{\"user\": {\"id\": 5, \"email\": \"lazjingo9@gmail.com\", \"roles\": [\"admin\"], \"version\": 1, \"password\": \"$2b$10$HwCeSm1IE2CS55eo92dEquYUMYF48U7EGuVpdYjIlIomHHqIlidLe\", \"createdAt\": \"2025-03-25T18:21:31.031Z\", \"createdBy\": null, \"deletedAt\": null, \"deletedBy\": null, \"isDeleted\": false, \"updatedAt\": \"2025-03-25T18:21:31.031Z\", \"updatedBy\": null}, \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjUsInJvbGVzIjpbImFkbWluIl0sImlhdCI6MTc0MjkzMTQ4MywiZXhwIjoxNzQyOTM1MDgzfQ._nixqeoDroIV6vC6slcr-F-6j7zS-gOlpiy7ZQhx