INSERT INTO `facilities` VALUES (1,'2025-03-31 12:14:19.062147','2025-04-01 14:59:41.000000','2025-04-01 14:59:41.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,5,0,'THGF','Mugga Tours is a  team based in Uganda. It consists of nature enthusiasts, explorers, mountain lovers, climbers, bird watchers, trail enthusiasts, and more. We have all the energy and knowledge of the entire East African Region\'s every nook to create the most beautiful circuits. Our goal is to show you Uganda, Rwanda, Kenya and Tanzania in a different light, through hiking, of course, but also by exploring the great region’s tremendous rivers through canoeing, kayaking and tubbing its shores  meeting its cliffs through climbing sometimes falling off. For families, we offer lake or mountain stays that allow you to try out these activities for a day or a week. For us,  the essential thing is always to enable you to live and have  a magical experience, leaving our goals, we operate with traditional standards and values of the region, including direct customer contact and high level of personalized customer service with a mind full of images, memories, and lived moments!\n\nWhether you\'re alone, with family, or friends, our trips and courses are designed for non-specialists and led by professionals. They are accessible to everyone, from locals to foreigners, to beginners wanting to try an activity to practitioners wishing to safely discover the hidden corners of East Africa the region of Beauty.!\n','Our Mission,To be the best tour service provider in East Africa by delivering quality customer experience and exceeding our partners’ expectations.','https://cf.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max1024x768/516522395.jpg?k=a8abe92493d010239a64fc11c1c5e4e4a79e4d88846ae86bccf2e0f785ccab78&o=&hp=1','Vision,To operate with traditional standards and values of the region,including direct customer contact and high level of personalized customer service.'),(2,'2025-03-31 12:17:08.077192','2025-04-01 14:59:34.000000','2025-04-01 14:59:34.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,4,0,'RTEYUFGHJDFGHJER','Vision\nTo operate with traditional standards and values of the region, including direct customer contact and high level of personalized customer service.\n','Vision,To operate with traditional standards and values of the region,including direct customer contact and high level of personalized customer service.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRO0NyaPwI3JcEnS4VPwYXYNCNxw4xkYS3TtYbp3ETrySWrLmVh-XpNdVbnZXOuscKgPdU&usqp=CAU','Vision,To operate with traditional standards and values of the region,including direct customer contact and high level of personalized customer service.'),(3,'2025-04-01 14:59:25.591576','2025-04-01 15:38:01.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,4,0,'Songbird Safari Lodge & Campsite, Kasaese Uganda.','Songbird Safari Lodge & Campsite features a garden, terrace, a restaurant and bar in Katunguru. Among the facilities at this property are room service and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. Guests can enjoy mountain views.\nGuests at the resort can enjoy a continental breakfast.','Free parking,Free Wifi,Restaurant,Non-smoking rooms,Room service,Family rooms,Bar,Breakfast','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743519430/IMG_9701_mwqsi0.jpg','Breakfast: Good breakfast,Parking: On-site parking,Views: Balcony View,Garden view,Mountain view,Accessibility: Entire unit wheelchair accessible'),(4,'2025-04-01 15:06:46.751564','2025-04-01 15:31:06.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,4,0,'Hakuna Matata Lodge, Gisenyi Rwanda','Set in Gisenyi, Hakuna Matata Lodge offers free WiFi, and guests can enjoy a garden, a private beach area and a terrace. Some accommodation includes a balcony with mountain views, a fully equipped kitchen and a private bathroom with bidet.\nThe restaurant at the lodge serves American and French cuisine.\nA children\'s playground is available on site and fishing can be enjoyed within close proximity of Hakuna Matata Lodge.','Free WiFi,Airport shuttle,2 restaurants,Beachfront,Non-smoking rooms,Free parking','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743519977/HAKUNA_MATATA_GISENYI1_qspewb.jpg','Room service, Bar, Private beach area, Decent breakfast'),(5,'2025-04-01 15:18:43.655870','2025-04-01 15:36:15.000000',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,4,0,'Dan Stam Hotel, Arusha Tanzania','Set in Arusha, 12 km from Uhuru monument, Dan Stam Hotel offers accommodation with a garden, free private parking, a shared lounge and a bar. This 3-star hotel offers a concierge service and a tour desk. The accommodation provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi throughout the property.\n','Free WiFi,Airport shuttle,Free parking,Non-smoking rooms,Family rooms,Restaurant,Room service,Spa and wellness centre,Bar,Breakfast','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743521771/dam_stam_hotel2_mxkb9n.jpg','Spa and wellness centre,Massage'),(6,'2025-04-01 15:25:36.124068','2025-04-01 15:25:36.124068',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,'KANUNKA HOUSE','Situated in Sekenani, KANUNKA HOUSE features accommodation with a hot tub, beauty services and a steam room. There is an in-house restaurant and free private parking. The guest house has family rooms as well as facilities for disabled guests.\n\nAt the guest house, every unit is equipped with a balcony. Complete with a private bathroom fitted with a bath and slippers, all units at the guest house have a flat-screen TV and air conditioning, and certain rooms come with a terrace. In some units there is a dressing room for guests to change in.','Free parking,Restaurant,Non-smoking rooms,Facilities for disabled guests,Room service,Family rooms,Tea/coffee maker in all rooms,Breakfast','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743521127/kanunka_house_sky1vt.jpg','Wellness,Hot tub/Jacuzzi, Massage');
