es, with a focus on local ingredients, spices, and traditional cooking methods.','FULL DAY',1.00,'Mon,Tue,Wed,Thur,Fri,Sat,Sun','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743690102/MUGGA_Wallpaper_PNG_8_qccsiq.png',1,20,'activity'),(30,'2025-04-03 14:27:08.258019','2025-04-03 14:27:08.258019',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,'CANOPY WALK','Canopy walk: Explore Uganda\'s Mabira Forest or Kenya\'s Kakamega Forest treetops, discovering the secrets of the forest canopy.','FULL DAY',1.00,'Mon,Tue,Wed,Thur,Fri,Sat,Sun','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743690297/IMG_9681_1111_j4xlie.jpg',1,20,'activity'),(31,'2025-04-03 14:28:23.038829','2025-04-03 14:28:23.038829',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,'SUN RISE SUN SET','Sunrise and sunset safaris: Witness the golden hours in Kenya\'s Amboseli National Park or Tanzania\'s Serengeti National Park, a truly unforgettable experience.','FULL DAY',1.00,'Mon,Tue,Wed,Thur,Fri,Sat,Sun','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743690496/wp13701435-beach-sunset_djwyuo.jpg',1,20,'activity'),(32,'2025-04-03 14:31:17.318395','2025-04-03 14:31:17.318395',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,'HOT AIR BALOON','Hot air balloon safaris: Drift above the savannas and grasslands at sunrise, taking in breathtaking views.','FULL DAY',1.00,'Mon,Tue,Wed,Thur,Fri,Sat,Sun','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743690651/wp4413540-magical-hot-air-balloon_121212_dyyl2i.jpg',1,20,'activity'),(33,'2025-04-03 14:42:59.720845','2025-04-03 14:42:59.720845',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,'HOTSPRINGS','Hot spring therapy: Relax in Tanzania\'s Lake Natron natural hot springs, rejuvenating body and mind.','FULL DAY',1.00,'Mon,Tue,Wed,Thur,Fri,Sat,Sun','https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1743691204/KASESE_HOT_SPRING_o6y3yb.jpg',1,20,'activity'),(34,'2025-04-11 12:19:12.328728','2025-04-11 12:19:12.328728',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,'MUGGA TROUPE ','Mugga Troupe is a dynamic and energetic African dancing troupe that showcases traditional and modern African dance styles. With intricate footwork, mesmerizing rhythms, and captivating costumes, we entertain audiences with their vibrant performances. There no better way to experience Africa’s vast cultural diversity than through dance. East Africa has more 5 counties with over 500 subcultures, and its dances provide an important link to the past. Traditional dances signify important events and convey emotions of love, sorrow, joy, and excitement. These dances vary in style from one region to the other and are an expression of each region’s way of life, beliefs, and norms.','4 hours ',1.00,'Mon,Tue,Wed,Thur,Fri,Sat,Sun','http://www.muggatours.com/',1,20,'services');
